// Windows application icon resource.
//
// The path is substituted by CMake's configure_file() as a native absolute path
// (see CMakeLists.txt), because the MSVC resource compiler (rc.exe) resolves
// relative ICON paths against its working directory, not the .rc file's
// directory. An absolute path makes the embedded icon independent of the
// build working directory.
IDI_ICON1 ICON "@MUFFIN_APP_ICON_ICO@"
